name: I Hate People
description:
I Hate People, a FNAF parody that has no swearing whatsoever.

This is a censored version of a game I made which I most likely will not release due to the content that I had to censor in this game as well as the original title.

In this game you play as Elmo, after having a wild party you pass out and wake up in an office building with a bunch of idiots, and you're the 4th.

Music in this game is from Party in Backyard.
